column5: Got out for 4 hours with the son today. Off to a quiet back water for some quality perch.  In the end 6 nice fish for what was a slow bite
Those are fatties Bruce.  I got out as well. Dang cold ,and the snow was,well,ya know.LOL
Nice little piggys Bruce !!! I didnt get many last season. I concentrated on walleye and Musky most of the time. Will definately set aside a day for those this year.
